    """

    # Apply filters
    filtered_data = (
        [item for item in data if all(f(item) for f in filters)]
        if filters else data
    )

    # Sort data
    sorted_data = sorted(filtered_data, key=sort_by) if sort_by else filtered_data

    # Aggregate if needed
    if not aggregate:
        return sorted_data

    for item in sorted_data:

        aggregated_data.setdefault(key, []).append(item)
